    "# Perceptron"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Pseudo code\n",
    "```\n",
    "perceptron(X, y) ->\n",
    "    while not converged:\n",
    "        if sign(w_t.x) != y_t:\n",
    "            $$w_{t+1} = w_t + a y_t x_t$$\n",
    "```"
   ]
